\columnbreak

> #### It Ain't Easy, Being a Machine
> As constructs, mechagnomes have additional difficulties that other races do not have to deal with. They are unaffected by a number of spells both harmful and beneficial. Players should be aware of the difficulties that come with the decision to play a character of this race. 
>
> <br> You are unaffected by the following spells.
