> ***Shadow Strike.*** As a bonus action, the arakkoa can expend a spell slot to cause its melee weapon attacks to magically deal an extra 10 (3d6) psychic damage to a target on a hit. This benefit lasts until the end of the turn. If the arakkoa expends a spell slot of 2nd level or higher, the extra damage increases by 1d6 for each level above 1st.
>
> ***Spellcasting.*** The arakkoa is a 5th-level spellcaster. Its spellcasting ability is Wisdom (spell save DC 13, +4 to hit with spell attacks). It has the following spells prepared:
>
> Cantrips (at will): *minor illusion, ✦ shadow bolt, <br/>&nbsp; thaumaturgy*
> <br/> 1st level (4 slots): *✦ dark void, mage armor, silent image*
> <br/> 2nd level (3 slots): *darkness, shadow blade ^XGE^*
> <br/> 3rd level (2 slots): *bestow curse, major image* 

